section.def:
Council
                (職訓局) means the Vocational Training Council
            established by section 4;

industry
                (工業、工業界)
            includes commerce and services;

trade
                (行業) means any trade or occupation in
            industry;

paragraph.content:
consider and approve, if thought fit, recommendations from training boards
                    and general committees for training courses;
                    and

consult with the Government and with any interested person on any matter
                    pertaining to technical education, industrial training or skills
                    training;

conduct or commission research into any aspect of technical education,
                    industrial training or skills
                    training;

receive and consider suggestions or proposals for the development of
                    technical education, industrial training and skills
                    training;

establish, operate and maintain technical colleges, technical institutes,
                    industrial training centres and skills
                    centres;

provide or approve training courses and other facilities for technical
                    education, industrial training and skills
                    training;

help candidates for industrial training and skills training to find
                    suitable training
                    facilities;
